Arenada: It's not afraid of..

00:16:13.714 --> 00:16:15.952
Anderson: No. we're definitely
not on the danger radar.

00:16:15.961 --> 00:16:17.399
The pumas don't care at all.

00:16:17.474 --> 00:16:19.072
This is the one
place in the world

