Anderson: The cats back
home would have run

00:26:01.314 --> 00:26:03.519
At these guys a long time ago.

00:26:09.874 --> 00:26:11.439
Arenada: It's gonna happen
at any moment.

00:26:14.441 --> 00:26:15.552
Now. now.

