Look how low she is.

00:26:42.034 --> 00:26:44.559
She's basically
doing a belly crawl.

00:26:52.841 --> 00:26:55.399
Uh-oh. up on. the one up
top might have busted her.

00:26:56.354 --> 00:26:57.552
Arenada: Not yet.

