A difficult weapon for
guanacos to defend against.

00:28:23.561 --> 00:28:25.319
Under the cloak of darkness.

00:28:25.394 --> 00:28:27.439
Pumas have their
greatest success.

00:28:29.874 --> 00:28:34.839
(gentle music)
(birds chirping)

